item.title: About
item.description: My names Waleed. I’m a student of BS Computer Science from FAST Islamabad. I’m currently in my final year. I’ve created this blog to write about all CS concepts i’ve learned in my 4 year degree. Furthermore, i shall attempt to cover newer topics which i may learn later on after my degree.

item.title: Hello World!!!!
item.description: Hello!! This is my first blog. I’m excited to write many more. I created this blog as part of a project for one of my CS courses. This course was MMDS (Mining Massive Datasets). We had to create a website and perform SEO (Search Engine Optimization) on it. Expect a few blogs about SEO in this space.
